t: bold; line-height: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0; position: relative;"=
><strong>Aggregators and Industrials</strong><span>&#160;</span></h3><p sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 20px 0;"><span>Anduril, Solugen, and Monumental Labs are just three exam=
ples, and all three are still relatively early in the journey. Most of the =
promise of Techno-Industrials as it stands lies in spreadsheets and </span>=
<a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/0e4e2f45-7a3c-4403-b27f-43b2c1c8fb=
