color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20p=
x 0;">Reasoning about Techno-Industrials requires us to go back further in =
time, all the way back to the Industrial Revolution in America. I&#8217;m c=
